\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_Canada\", \"score\": 0.9671142878994102, \"rank\": 0.02935758753387155, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 733, \"end\": 739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.999119107030347, \"rank\": 0.0008698677171486797, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 828, \"end\": 838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\", \"score\": 0.9999999912251951, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Edith Piaf\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It markedDion's first performance since 2022,when she was forced to cancel her world tour after being diagnosed with Stiff Person Syndrome, a rare and incurable disorder that causes rigidity in the torso and limbs, along with painful muscle spasms.\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 1111, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the concert, she wore a glittering white gown as she sang in front of a grand piano while the rain poured down around her.\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1238, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\\"My Heart Will Go On\\\" star has previously said that, at its worst, the condition makes it feel as though someone is pushing down on her larynx and pharynx when she is trying to sing.\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1426, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the weekend, she shared a number of glowing reactions to her Paris show, including an ESPN post that shared a photo of her as a teenager standing in front of the Eiffel Tower, alongside one of her singing underneath it as an adult.\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1664, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1494, \"end\": 1499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5811784292505173e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1519, \"end\": 1523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"score\": 0.999999996691713, \"rank\": 3.2301184833751263e-09, \"text\": \"ESPN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The image was captioned: \\\"How it started... How it's going.\\\"\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1726, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dion, 56, made the pledge in her recent documentary that she would one day return to Paris, as she was filmed during rehabilitation and singing sessions.\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1881, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1813, \"end\": 1818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5811784292505173e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The throwback photo also featured, along with a number of archive clips of her as an aspiring artist.\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1983, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In an earlier Instagram post, Dion said that she was \\\"full of joy\\\" to be back in one of her favourite cities.\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 2094, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1999, \"end\": 2008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2963871881697357e-37, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Most of all, I am 