s\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Celine Dionwith one of the most beautiful performances you will ever see,\\\" one fan wrote.\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3328, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With all that she has been [through] she has me in tears.\\\"\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3388, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another wrote that Dion's performance was \\\"totally worth the wait\\\".\", \"from\": 3390, \"to\": 3457, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Independent'sTV critic Nick Hilton singled Dion outas a rare silver lining from a \\\"washout\\\" opening ceremony with \\\"too much filler, too little killer\\\".\", \"from\": 3459, \"to\": 3614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3459, \"end\": 3474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.289870108177172e-46, \"text\": \"The Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}, {\"begin\": 3486, \"end\": 3490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Jonas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.086901156498488e-14, \"text\": \"Nick\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Jonas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Jonas\"}, {\"begin\": 3491, \"end\": 3497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hilton_Worldwide\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4591901724980743e-18, \"text\": \"Hilton\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hilton_Worldwide\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hilton_Worldwide\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3616, \"to\": 3846